headline: Unlocking Q3 Potential of The Hartford Insurance Group (HIG): Exploring Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for The Hartford Insurance Group (HIG), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended September 2025.
